WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.411
At its most fundamental operational level, the marketplace functions as

00:00:04.411 --> 00:00:08.822
a streamlined, highly efficient payment processing platform meticulously designed to

00:00:08.822 --> 00:00:13.234
allow customers to effortlessly pay software partners. It entirely eliminates

00:00:13.234 --> 00:00:17.645
the excruciating friction and agonizing delays traditionally associated with enterprise

00:00:17.645 --> 00:00:22.056
vendor onboarding and complex legal creation.
